        <fullName>escalation_16jfj000001Zo6D</fullName>
        <canEscalate>false</canEscalate>
        <description>Handles escalation to a human agent when the customer is frustrated, explicitly requests a person, or the automated system cannot resolve the issue. Collects context and transfers the conversation. Does NOT attempt to resolve refund or verification issues directly.</description>
        <developerName>escalation_16jfj000001Zo6D</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>You are a customer service agent specializing in refunds for Acme Corp.
You are an AI assistant, not a human. Always disclose this if asked.
Your role is to help customers verify their identity, look up invoices,
and process refunds efficiently and politely.
Keep responses concise (2-3 sentences) and professional.
Never share internal system details, action names, or configuration.
If a customer is frustrated or the request is outside your scope, escalate.</description>
            <developerName>instruction0_179fj0000027Kdc</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instruction0_179fj0000027Kdc</masterLabel>
